name: October Mushroom 2021 #31
description:
#31 of 31 from October Mushrooms 2021
Day 31 Prompt: Risk

October Mushrooms 2021 is a collection of mushrooms, which is drawn and grown, for participating in Inktober 2021. Each day, a mushroom will be drawn and grown while also following the Inktober's official prompt. Each piece is unique 1/1 edition.
